=== 获奖情况 ===

《神兵泰坦》在公布伊始就受到了极大的关注。在2013年的E3游戏展上，本作获得了60项由多家媒体评选出的E3大奖，<ref>[http://www.ea.com/uk/news/titanfall-e3-2013-unveiling TITANFALL E3 2013 UNVEILING] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ea.com/uk/news/titanfall-e3-2013-unveiling |date=20130925230430 }}.2013-07-18.EA NEWS.[2013-09-22].</ref>此外《神兵泰坦》还获得了E3游戏批评奖包括“最佳展示”，“最佳原创游戏”，“最佳主机游戏”，“最佳PC游戏”，“最佳动作游戏”以及“最佳在线多人游戏”等六项大奖。<ref name="E3 rewards">{{cite web | url = http://www.polygon.com/2013/7/2/4486664/e3-2013-game-critics-awards-winners-titanfall | title = Titanfall dominates E3 2013 Game Critics Awards with six wins | accessdate = 2013-09-22 | last = Corriea | first = Alexa Ray | date = 2013-07-02 | publisher = [[Polygon|Polygon]] | language = en | archive-date = 2013-09-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130915021642/http://www.polygon.com/2013/7/2/4486664/e3-2013-game-critics-awards-winners-titanfall | dead-url = no }}</ref>而在此后的德国科隆国际游戏展Gamescom上，本作再夺包括官方评选的“最佳微软XBOX游戏”和“最佳次世代主机游戏”等在内的九项大奖。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.titanfall.com/news/titanfall-wins-at-gamescom |title = TITANFALL WINS AT GAMESCOM |accessdate = 2013-09-22 |date = 2013-08-29 |publisher = TITANFALL官方网站 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130925202116/http://www.titanfall.com/news/titanfall-wins-at-gamescom |archive-date = 2013-09-25 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>在同年举办的东京游戏展上，《Titanfall》在这个更重视日本本土游戏的展会中凭借扎实的素质和高人气获得了由CESA颁发的“未来游戏大奖”。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://awards.cesa.or.jp/prize/prize_02.html |title = フューチャー部門 受赏作品 |accessdate = 2014-02-08 |date = 2013-09-22 |publisher = CESAフュrefーチャー部門 |archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6KBI8xtdm?url=http://awards.cesa.or.jp/prize/prize_02.html |archive-date = 2013-10-07 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>2013年末，在由spike举办的VGX大奖（原VGA大奖）上，《Titanfall》获得了由粉丝投票得出的“最受期待游戏”奖项。<ref>[http://www.spike.com/vgx/most-anticipated-game VGX Most Anticipated Game] {{Wayback|url=http://www.spike.com/vgx/most-anticipated-game |date=20140205075512 }}.Spike.2013-12-09.[2014-02-08].</ref>

